From: Bruce Ashfield <bruce.ashfield@windriver.com>
Date: Tue, 21 Oct 2008 12:31:14 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] Add updated drm headers files to export list

The *plus* files that are included by the stock header
files also need to be exported in order to produce a
valid set of userspace includes.

Signed-off-by: Bruce Ashfield <bruce.ashfield@windriver.com>
---
 include/drm/Kbuild |    7 +++++++
 1 files changed, 7 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/include/drm/Kbuild b/include/drm/Kbuild
index 82b6983..8e7be73 100644
--- a/include/drm/Kbuild
+++ b/include/drm/Kbuild
@@ -8,3 +8,10 @@ unifdef-y += radeon_drm.h
 unifdef-y += sis_drm.h
 unifdef-y += savage_drm.h
 unifdef-y += via_drm.h
+unifdef-y += r300_reg.h 
+unifdef-y += via_3d_reg.h
+unifdef-y += mach64_drm.h 
+unifdef-y += nouveau_drm.h
+unifdef-y += via_drm_plus.h
+unifdef-y += i915_drm_plus.h
+unifdef-y += drm_plus.h
